WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.250
Integrating the conditional density produces
the conditional distribution.

00:00:04.350 --> 00:00:08.200
Here, for each ordered year, the surface gives
the estimated share

00:00:08.200 --> 00:00:12.550
of Italian regions with per-capita GDP
at or below each value.

00:00:12.550 --> 00:00:17.300
One npcdist() call estimates
the whole conditional distribution.

00:00:17.300 --> 00:00:22.550
Invert the conditional distribution at a chosen probability
and you obtain a conditional quantile.

00:00:22.550 --> 00:00:25.000
The full script is on Gallery Video Demos.
